{"tid":2245692,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"小學生坐巴士誤投$270 焦急大哭 巴士司機暖心舉動讓妹妹感激道謝","createTime":"2020-10-16T12:04:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-16T12:47:47.000Z","uid":36494,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"7923068e0d601d3462524c287425b837139d820c","tid":2245692,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T12:04:19.000Z","msg":"幾百元對成人來說也不是一個小數目，更何況小朋友！台灣一名小學女生早前放學坐巴士回家，上車入錢時，不小心把手上的10元台幣及一張1000元台幣（約港幣$270）一起投進去，小妹妹在車內焦急地哭了起來，巴士司機見狀，想到了一個權宜之計，讓小妹妹收起眼淚開心地說謝謝。<br />\n<br />\n從當時公車內畫面可見，司機一見到小妹妹誤投鈔票，立即提醒她，可是已經太遲了。小妹妹表示那張1000元是一周的餐費，要交給補習社，但因無法當場開起錢箱，焦急得在車上哭了起來，司機透過電話和小女孩家人說明情況，表示要先將她載回總站，但礙於開啟投幣箱有程序要執行，必須等翌日才能拿出裏面的錢。<br />\n<br />\n司機也不斷安撫小妹妹，多次說「不要哭，沒有事」，一旁乘客也安慰妹妹「沒事喔！趕快先坐好」。後來妹妹到總站後邊走邊哭，令人不捨，因為許姓司機還要繼續開車，就先行離開。<br />\n<br />\n另一位在站內待命的巴士司機見狀後，實在不忍心，於是馬上先行墊錢給小妹妹，自己再等公司開錢箱，這時小妹妹才收起眼淚開心地說謝謝後安心離去。<br />\n<br />\n好心司機表示當時準備出車，看到小女孩一下車就站在路邊一直哭，眼淚一直流，發現不對勁，就問她發生甚麼事，才知道她不小心把一千元鈔票丟進錢箱。「我於心不忍，所以墊錢再看看翌日怎樣處理，然後再安撫小女孩，後來她也不斷說謝謝才離開。」"},{"pid":"f1673173a0c8285e41f6a9d44e3d1809cae681d5","tid":2245692,"uid":181789,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T12:05:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港司機都好好"},{"pid":"9a2118e712ec468916b4d97b20d17b28ed5392e7","tid":2245692,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T12:14:32.000Z","msg":"見鬼喇我也哭了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca8e54549c980db767976a792ea417e277830667","tid":2245692,"uid":96704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T12:39:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb710201e1f39382528059cd7a9612af7efb56e6","tid":2245692,"uid":250036,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f1673173a0c8285e41f6a9d44e3d1809cae681d5","tid":2245692,"uid":181789,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T12:05:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港司機都好好"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T12:39:10.000Z","msg":"可能會趕佢落車，再唔係call防暴"},{"pid":"2bdd662817d3e4118a509303f873a2674f10d7da","tid":2245692,"uid":28068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T12:40:08.000Z","msg":"圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45657b27484f0763e6205de6d41145483e7d792f","tid":2245692,"uid":268516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T12:41:02.000Z","msg":"係咪新北市<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc7110db078e2a1afaa0222d9066c7cfbf318125","tid":2245692,"uid":103809,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T12:41:05.000Z","msg":"好耐之前有單小學雞斯斯然入500蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b70e7a5db0c53473da494bd934f069976408820","tid":2245692,"uid":103809,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T12:41:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20150113/CRYUTQGDVSMQQLM5T7Y2AXPFJI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20150113%2FCRYUTQGDVSMQQLM5T7Y2AXPFJI%2F&d=Z58AETknIeTPCCdXMCOVU%2BdFAmKeyJhstBKVrdqrVyA%3D&h=52811265\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20150113%2FCRYUTQGDVSMQQLM5T7Y2AXPFJI%2F&h=34e3cd63\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20150113/CRYUTQGDVSMQQLM5T7Y2AXPFJI/</a>"},{"pid":"69417638780f1859092713ecd1551237577070b6","tid":2245692,"uid":308486,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T12:42:29.000Z","msg":"反觀香港之前唔係有個小學生勁豪爽扔張500蚊落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b8d146f3ce70945d74105d5722a137be531d53a","tid":2245692